race.description: The Wharf Mooloolaba Swiss Ace Plate
race.comment: The $125,000 Swiss Ace Plate. HIDDEN WEALTH (1) was very competitive in Group company when last in work and should find this assignment a touch easier. Revved up for this with two solid trials and has a bit of class over most of these. Sure to be right there at the business end. PARTY FOR TWO (13) has put three victories together and is racing with a lot of confidence of late. Hard to ignore winning form. Former NSW galloper LONHRO'S QUEEN (16) returned in fine fashion with a strong win when having the first run for the new stable and will have come on with that run now in the locker. Top-three candidate. NETTUNO (5) draws the inside alley and gets the deadly Gollan/Maloney combination. In the mix. FLEETWOOD (7) best of the rest while fresh.
